data.description: Welcome to Cape Crossroads community. This beautifully updated end unit offers 3 bedrooms, including a primary suite with a walk-in closet,and 2 full bathrooms. Enjoy the sun filled open concept living/dining/kitchen with new flooring throughout, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops and island as well as a stackable washer/dryer. The HOA fee includes a pool, tennis, basketball, master insurance, landscaping, snow removal, trash removal and common areas. Enjoy the convenience of this prime location close to restaurants, shopping, medical center and hospital. Experience comfort and style in this charming condo. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home or rental property!
